version_description:
- We've added more cute Squishies for you to Paint, Squish and Collect!
- New Squishy Selection Gallery to help you choose which Squishy you want to color next!

- We've added more cute Squishies for you to Paint, Squish and Collect!
- New Color Palettes: Rainbow Giraffe and Camouflage! 
- Daily Rewards! Open them and get exciting Squishies and Color Palettes!
- We fixed a very annoying bug that caused crashes on older devices.

- New Squishies for you to Paint, Squish and Collect: Princess, Chocolate Bar, Bee and many more!
- New Color Palettes: Sand, Peach, Metal Scales and more!

New! Choose Backgrounds for your Squishies: Will it be a Bubble Gum color or a 3D Underwater scene?
More Squishies: Try the new House Squishy or maybe a Peacock? Come to think of it, why choose? just try them all...
New "My Squishies" screen design: Store your custom creations complete with a Background and a name tag.

- New Squishies: Fish, Alarm Clock, Milkshake and more!
- More Beautiful Backgrounds for you to choose from and get in your daily new packs.
- Even more new Palettes for endless squishy coloring possibilities.

- More Squishies! Rainbow Heart, Galaxy Heart, Teapot, Caterpillar, Shooting Star, Galaxy Cow and a few more surprises...
- More Beautiful Backgrounds for you to choose from and get in your daily new packs.
- Even more new Palettes for endless squishy coloring possibilities.

- New game mode: My Squishy Shop!
- New Squishies: Russian Doll and Emoji squishies.
- You can now set your favorite squishy as your device wallpaper.
- New palette: Marble.
- New background: Eggplant.

New Squishies - New mochi rubbery stretchy squishies! and more...
New Glossy Galaxy Palette.
New Backgrounds - Butterflies and Sunset.

You can now get surprise packs by making new Squishies!
New Squishies - Mermaid and Mochi Chicken.
New Cherry Backgrounds.

Holiday Themed Surprises: Snowman Squishy and tons of new holiday backgrounds: Snowy Mountains, Candy and many more!
For a limited time: a special Moriah Elizabeth squishy pack containing 6 original squishies!
New 3-in-1 Special Offers: get 1 Squishy, 1 Palette and 1 Background bundles!

New Squishies - Tiger and Smirking Emoji.
New Backgrounds - Chocolate Cake, Raspberry Jello and Birthday Cake.

New Monkey Squishy!
New palette navigation UI

• It's finally here:  Unicorn Cake Squishy. 
• 3 New color palettes: Leopard, Bronze, Neon Shapes.
• 2 New backgrounds from beyond: Celestial, Stardust.

• New rodent arrives: Hamster Squishy.
• New fashionable palette: Diamond Sweater.
• 3 New backgrounds: Dreamy Flowers, Green Cactus, Pink Cactus.

New squishy: Sloth!
Fresh new Look & Feel for the app!

New squishy: CupBear! How Cute!
Various interface enhancements and bug fixes.
